.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, helicopter, tram, bike, boat
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the british is the person who likes red
2. the swedish is the owner of the dog
3. the danish is the person drinking tea
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person drinking coffee
6. the person driving the tram is the owner of the bird
7. the person who likes yellow is the person driving the helicopter
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter
12. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking beer
13. the german is the person driving the bike
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Transport		|   helicopter	|    boat	|  tram	|    bike	|   skateboard	|
